      "order": 1,
      "Description": "This lesson explores the confidentiality risks that arise when using AI tools in professional environments where sensitive client data is involved. You will learn how financial, legal, and personal information can be inadvertently exposed when inputting data into AI systems, and why this matters for your clients and your organisation. We will look at practical steps you can take to protect client confidentiality while still benefiting from AI in your day-to-day work. By the end of this lesson, you will have a clearer understanding of your responsibilities and the simple habits that can help you avoid costly data breaches.",
